Total costs (watering and feeding) = 13 * $3 = $39
Net profit from lemons = $136.5 - $39 = $97.5
Initial planting cost = $90
Total profit = $97.5 - $90 = $7.5. He has started earning money.

The final answer is $\boxed{13}$

